WEBVTT

00:08.40 --> 00:09.40
- Hey!

00:09.80 --> 00:10.30
- My name is Xavier

00:11.80 --> 00:13.40
- and I'm a car enthusiast.

00:13.90 --> 00:15.50
- I enjoy anything car related

00:16.00 --> 00:18.10
- whether it's basic maintenance

00:18.60 --> 00:20.60
- like a simple tire rotation

00:21.10 --> 00:22.80
- or custom modifications

00:23.20 --> 00:24.60
- like an air intake system.

00:26.00 --> 00:28.50
- This is my 2015 Honda Civic EX. 

00:29.00 --> 00:30.60 
- It may not be the quickest car

00:31.10 --> 00:33.50
- but it's been nothing short of amazing.

